187
00:13:22,053 --> 00:13:24,322
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau mencintaiku?</font>

188
00:13:24,893 --> 00:13:28,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga mencintaimu. Aku mencintaimu.</font>

189
00:13:31,533 --> 00:13:34,133
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan pergi. Tetap bersamaku.</font>

190
00:13:35,763 --> 00:13:37,362
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

191
00:13:44,712 --> 00:13:45,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mencari seseorang?</font>

192
00:13:45,872 --> 00:13:48,543
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, seseorang yang membuatku gugup.</font>

193
00:13:48,543 --> 00:13:50,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan dengan jelas.</font>

194
00:13:50,313 --> 00:13:52,813
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia mengganggumu,
