195
00:13:52,913 --> 00:13:54,253
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu hal yang pasti.</font>

196
00:13:54,253 --> 00:13:56,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada seseorang yang selalu menggangguku.</font>

197
00:13:56,622 --> 00:13:59,192
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Siapa orang itu?</font>

198
00:13:59,192 --> 00:14:01,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan. Siapa?/ Kau!</font>

199
00:14:02,962 --> 00:14:04,633
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau siapa?</font>

200
00:14:05,433 --> 00:14:08,362
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kalian berdua penipu?/ Maaf.</font>

201
00:14:08,663 --> 00:14:11,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami reporter./ Sungguh?</font>

202
00:14:11,803 --> 00:14:14,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Reporter zaman sekarang tidak
