236
00:17:01,072 --> 00:17:03,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini kamar wanita!</font>

237
00:17:03,072 --> 00:17:06,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak peduli.
Kamar pria sedang direnovasi...</font>

238
00:17:06,243 --> 00:17:09,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang dulu tidur di bawah selimut ini.</font>

239
00:17:09,582 --> 00:17:12,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudmu aku yang
mengikutmu tidur disini?</font>

240
00:17:12,352 --> 00:17:14,882
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memang gila./
Kakimu diatas tubuhku!</font>

241
00:17:14,882 --> 00:17:17,053
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menyentuh kakiku?</font>

242
00:17:18,053 --> 00:17:19,993
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat aneh.</font>

243
00:17:27,463 --> 00:17:28,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

244
00:17:32,072 --> 00:17:34,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Tersangka pembunuhan Jo Hang Joon?
Apa dia melakukannya sendiri?</font>

245
00:17:34,872 --> 00:17:36,303
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya bukti?</font>

246
00:17:38,372 --> 00:17:40,112
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingat apa yang aku katakan?</font>

247
00:17:40,112 --> 00:17:42,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudmu, aku menganggu?</font>

248
00:17:44,313 --> 00:17:45,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai nanti.</font>

249
00:17:46,652 --> 00:17:48,283
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bicara nanti.</font>

250
00:17:48,953 --> 00:17:50,053
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tunggu.</font>

251
00:17:53,892 --> 00:17:54,963
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dimana?</font>

252
00:17:56,693 --> 00:17:59,063
<font color=#FFFF00>Awasi Gong Soo Chang.</font>

253
00:17:59,693 --> 00:18:02,932
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Mari kita lihat barangnya.</font>

254
00:18:05,503 --> 00:18:08,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita sering melakukan ini. Cepat.</font>

255
00:18:08,372 --> 00:18:11,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena sering melakukan ini,
aku harus berhati-hati.</font>

256
00:18:11,473 --> 00:18:12,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lucu.</font>

257
00:18:42,273 --> 00:18:43,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Perhatikan jalanmu!</font>

258
00:19:02,162 --> 00:19:03,592
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir, minggir!</font>

259
00:19:06,632 --> 00:19:08,063
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir!</font>

260
00:19:08,602 --> 00:19:09,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir.</font>

261
00:19:20,713 --> 00:19:21,783
<font color=#FFFF00>Cari kesana.</font>

262
00:19:34,662 --> 00:19:37,392
<font color=#FFFF00>Buruk. Hari yang buruk.</font>

263
00:19:57,382 --> 00:20:00,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda ditangkap karena membunuh seorang detektif.</font>

264
00:20:00,682 --> 00:20:03,223
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda punya hak untuk membawa
pengacara dan tetap diam...</font>

265
00:20:03,223 --> 00:20:05,953
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, tunggu, tunggu.
Apa yang kau bicarakan?</font>

266
00:20:05,953 --> 00:20:07,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Membunuh detektif?</font>

267
00:20:07,993 --> 00:20:10,193
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau membunuhnya?/
Detektif Cha!</font>

268
00:20:11,263 --> 00:20:12,362
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lakukan itu.</font>

269
00:20:23,503 --> 00:20:24,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak akan kemana-mana.</font>

270
00:20:25,072 --> 00:20:27,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meninggalkan kunci di kantor polisi.</font>

271
00:20:27,372 --> 00:20:29,642
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia menyetir ke tempat lain
