272
00:20:31,553 --> 00:20:33,182
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan menembaknya.</font>

273
00:20:33,453 --> 00:20:35,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak./ Kau dengar itu?</font>

274
00:20:35,822 --> 00:20:37,592
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu memegang kata-katanya.</font>

275
00:20:37,592 --> 00:20:38,993
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh tidak...</font>

276
00:20:38,993 --> 00:20:41,493
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Tak, dia tersenyum.</font>

277
00:20:44,592 --> 00:20:45,932
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan tunjukkan gigimu.</font>

278
00:20:45,932 --> 00:20:47,733
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan pukul wajahku.</font>

279
00:20:48,332 --> 00:20:51,003
<font color=#FFFF00>Kulihat ada rumah sakit di sana.
Obati bahumu.</font>

280
00:20:51,003 --> 00:20:52,733
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja?/
Dan kembali.</font>

281
00:20:52,872 --> 00:20:54,342
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, sampai nanti.</font>

282
00:21:03,513 --> 00:21:05,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia kuat juga untuk seukuran
wanita cantik.</font>

283
00:21:11,352 --> 00:21:13,122
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bicara tentang pembunuhan.</font>

284
00:21:13,892 --> 00:21:17,122
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang aku bunuh?</font>

285
00:21:17,493 --> 00:21:20,463
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudku, kau salah orang.</font>

286
00:21:20,832 --> 00:21:23,162
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang membuatmu berpikir
kalau aku akan membunuh...</font>

287
00:21:23,162 --> 00:21:24,533
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

288
00:21:24,872 --> 00:21:27,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Jo Hang Joon, rekanku./ Apa?</font>

289
00:21:28,572 --> 00:21:29,703
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa? Siapa?</font>

290
00:21:31,273 --> 00:21:34,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu kau bilang akan balas dendam
setelah keluar.</font>

291
00:21:35,983 --> 00:21:36,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga...</font>

292
00:21:36,983 --> 00:21:39,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang saksi melihatmu di tempat kejadian.</font>

293
00:21:39,813 --> 00:21:42,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Saksi?/ Kau tahu apa artinya?</font>

294
00:21:43,553 --> 00:21:45,122
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pembunuh.</font>

295
00:21:45,122 --> 00:21:48,693
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan aku. Itu sungguh bukan aku.</font>

296
00:21:49,023 --> 00:21:52,793
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan aku. Aku sungguh tidak melakukannya.</font>

297
00:21:52,793 --> 00:21:54,932
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Teruslah bilang itu bukan kau.</font>

298
00:21:55,132 --> 00:21:56,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku benci kalau kau menyerah.</font>

299
00:21:56,632 --> 00:21:59,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini gila.</font>

300
00:21:59,973 --> 00:22:02,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, jadi masalahnya sekarang...</font>

301
00:22:02,503 --> 00:22:03,773
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa mereka?</font>

302
00:22:09,142 --> 00:22:11,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau berhutang sesuatu pada mereka?/
Bukankah kau?</font>

303
00:23:06,172 --> 00:23:07,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kalian?</font>

304
00:23:09,043 --> 00:23:11,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku polisi yang sedang bertugas.</font>

305
00:23:12,172 --> 00:23:14,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian sedang mengancam polisi sekarang.</font>

306
00:23:19,082 --> 00:23:21,882
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa mereka tidak akan
membiarkan kita pergi.</font>

307
00:23:24,453 --> 00:23:27,322
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan melawannya?/
Kau bisa bertarung?</font>

308
00:23:32,662 --> 00:23:34,332
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan meminjam tubuhmu.</font>

309
00:23:34,432 --> 00:23:35,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

310
00:24:17,713 --> 00:24:18,813
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayolah!</font>

311
00:24:27,953 --> 00:24:29,122
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan bertanya untuk terakhir kali.</font>

312
00:24:29,483 --> 00:24:30,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan kau orangnya?</font>

313
00:24:30,622 --> 00:24:34,092
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memang penipu, tapi bukan pembunuh!</font>

314
00:26:19,963 --> 00:26:21,263
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hampir mati...</font>

315
00:26:23,602 --> 00:26:26,533
<font color=#FFFF00>...karena detektif sialan itu,</font>

316
00:26:27,572 --> 00:26:29,203
